{"title": "How to Create a Deceased Patient File", "body": "Submitting a patient as deceased can be easily updated in the Patients Profile:\nGo on To Patient Profile\nSelect Details, then Demographics\nInput the Date of Death, then Click save.\nNow you have successfully updated the Patient as Deceased on the Patient File\n\nPlease note that once a patient is deemed as deceased you will not be able to add notes, however, there are alternatives to adding information to a patient profile. If you would like to know how please click here:  Why can't I Add Notes to a Deceased Patient?\n "}